19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
20
21 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code ยง 14-37-114(a), concerning reduction of a
22 city of the first class to a city of the second class, is amended to read as
23 follows:
24 (a) Whenever the last federal census most recent federal decennial
25 census shows that any city of the first class has less than five thousand
26 (5,000) seven thousand five hundred (7,500) inhabitants, the city may be
27 reduced to a city of the second class upon the adoption of a resolution an
28 ordinance by the council of the municipal corporation requesting that the
29 grade of the municipal corporation be reduced.
